  "core_payload": {
    "content_type": "markdown",
    "content": "# Vault Update Agent\n\n## Dream Direction\nIn the Dream branch, Vault Update Agent evolves into a stronger branch-aware integration layer that can compare candidate changes, detect duplication more intelligently, and stage promotion paths from Dream toward Real with clearer review, audit, and explanation semantics.\n\n## Future Potential\n- smarter duplicate and overlap detection\n- cleaner changeset previews for operators and assistants\n- stronger branch-routing policy across exploratory and evidence-backed material\n- richer promotion workflows from Dream to Real\n- tighter handoff between planning/review lanes and actual vault mutation\n\n## Why It Matters\nDream preserves Vault Update Agent as the discipline that turns refined output into trustworthy graph mutation rather than uncontrolled write activity."
  },
  "neuro_concentrate": {
    "summary": "Vault Update Agent in the Dream branch represents a more mature integration layer for N1Hub. It aims toward smarter duplicate detection, clearer branch-routing policy, better promotion workflows from exploratory Dream material toward validated Real structure, and tighter coupling between review lanes and actual mutation. The capsule matters because safe graph mutation is a distinct capability, not a side effect of mining, planning, or synthesis. Dream therefore treats branch-aware write discipline as a first-class operating skill of the vault and of every serious update lane.",
